name: Husky Avax
description: The First and Original dog on Avalanche. First merchandise token on Avax! Husky Avax is a token that was stealth-launched on May 12th, 2021 and runs on the Avalanche C-Chain. It features locked initial liquidity, a hard-capped supply, has no team allocation, and will have no airdrops. Husky benefits immensely by running on Avalanche, where secure and decentralized transactions are fast, cheap, and environmentally friendly.
